        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You know how to talk down creatures of larger size from making the mistake of attacking your allies. You become trained in Intimidation, or you gain the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Intimidating Glare] skill feat if you were already trained. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your Intimidation checks to [[/act demoralize]] creatures of a larger size than you that attacked an ally since the beginning of your last turn.</p>"
